{
  "stem": "5228.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then my cousin, the oldest, just said, let them sleep here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She said, let them sleep of the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Just let them be here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then, it took us a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then we moved in, in Fernwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In the house, there was one couple, and two men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then we moved in with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And my husband start to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he worked already in hospital, there in Fernwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he brought, you know, such a-- to covering up a corner, from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that's what he put this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we was-- and we lived there, with them, together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we was staying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we didn't got where to go on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I just told my husband, [? where ?] we'll be the first registration.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I wanted gone out from here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I still remembered the-- from my brother, how he said, if you survive, go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Still it was Palestine this time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we didn't got where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And nobody was ready to take us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we was sitting in Fernwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And then we was free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Then was mine daughter was born in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I start just to complain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I don't want to be here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I couldn't stand-- I couldn't stand the Germans that used to coming in, and this, and this, and the German doctors to go on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I just-- I couldn't take it this more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I didn't want it more to be in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Then was-- the first registration was to Norway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we went there [INAUDIBLE], I didn't feel there too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "My husband always said-- I said that my daughter will not marry a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "It was-- it was not this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I told them this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I was thinking.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
